---
title: Pork Borek Filo Snail & Carrot Salad Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Unravel the layers of flavour hidden within this dish, with tender, spiced pork encased in
crunchy filo. Paired with a carrot salad and a side of tangy garlic yoghurt, this dish is a twist on tradition which is sure to please!

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving.*
